$ System.Management.Automation.ErrorRecord (class)

An instance of `System.Management.Automation.ErrorRecord` describes a → Windows/PowerShell/language/error-handling#ps-error-types[non-terminating PowerShell error].

In a `catch` block of a → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/try-catch-finally[`try` … `catch`] statement, the
→ Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/psItem[automatic variable `$_`] is an instance of of such an `ErrorRecord` object.

Note: `System.Management.Automation.ErrorRecord`
→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Management/Automation/InformationalRecord#InformationalRecord-inheritance[does not inherit from `System.Managment.Automation.InformationalRecord`].


